{"tid":1212620,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"連登=「表決大台」 指揮中心=「行動大台」","createTime":"2019-06-12T20:00:16.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-12T20:50:13.000Z","uid":154486,"like":17,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"52d34022700c0f876542bfa3415345dbabfeec1a","tid":1212620,"uid":154486,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T20:00:16.000Z","msg":"我突然間諗到一樣野：<br />\n大台 - 其實有兩種意思<br />\n<br />\n一、決定事件既走向，包括衝擊邊度、幾點衝擊、點解衝擊、進攻、撤退<br />\n二、實際上係戰場上既戰略同戰術調動、物資後援，又名戰術指揮系統<br />\n<br />\n(一)既話目前係由連登時事台集體表決<br />\n<br />\n咁(二) 既大台成立其實係唔會比人騎劫，因為(二) 只係去執行(一) 既命令<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n所以實質既大台可以存在，但係整體既控制話語權都係取決於連登時事台既表決"},{"pid":"c9191b0770f1fb2d0e8a42af36463419cbbb8b32","tid":1212620,"uid":154486,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T20:01:35.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"7c13ff764c0c555f7aa289a7ddea195a57431c72","tid":1212620,"uid":258409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T20:04:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4c4d782a39b6c4716d75651bf769bf04bfd1913f","tid":1212620,"uid":87264,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T20:05:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"238a38971f1d8bf3e41df8b37e8d75387951f736","tid":1212620,"uid":154486,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"7c13ff764c0c555f7aa289a7ddea195a57431c72","tid":1212620,"uid":258409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T20:04:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T20:07:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b4a0e6813b05a05e22efdb6e3af9eb6af208140c","tid":1212620,"uid":154486,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"4c4d782a39b6c4716d75651bf769bf04bfd1913f","tid":1212620,"uid":87264,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"repl